擊不破壞不入禁區<br />\n3. Be water<br />\n4. 促政府答應五大訴求<br />\n5. 停止暴力打壓示威遊行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">文宣有彩色、有黑白！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HJiNHkn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHJiNHkn.png&h=7aee2c58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ScTaC6X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FScTaC6X.png&h=c0322113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJvwnn8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJvwnn8.png&h=c9585c21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ogUdAH8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FogUdAH8.png&h=872516f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b06e43e4c01c223c10f21ef986fcb5934f2c1ee","tid":1429282,"uid":8922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T21:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2841e3755a4201bddb6aafd87173d2ca2ff0ba1","tid":1429282,"uid":230511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T21:37:25.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n如果見到支那人搞事記得大大聲用英文講This is Canada/其他<br />\n國家, I have my freedom"},{"pid":"38e497934dc6a49a40ea2e49d778f4c6afe8468f","tid":1429282,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T21:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66bb631cd183458584fe886de08f5524220d91f2","tid":1429282,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T21:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57069a07d0a88db22ee0fed1b672ed7cd617b891","tid":1429282,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T21:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f4f42d1f48dae403437d64437d14487c3a92f0","tid":1429282,"uid":170187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T22:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481ef81fdff5616b36ecb32685e4df872b29e4be","tid":1429282,"uid":170187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T23:17:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f6ba90293f5a82f78df97945c4af435d746643","tid":1429282,"uid":170187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:18:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc5cc237de602687b3cbfcd4b1b7b9a1b70e842","tid":1429282,"uid":272942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:23:22.000Z","msg":"好客之道"},{"pid":"c194fe2673d8632a640cc2f65f0f53b22bce1951","tid":1429282,"uid":108786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f08d0f3ebaa6fe965d073fda4315307de0590823","tid":1429282,"uid":170187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:55:00.000Z","msg":"【全球號召】香港機場接機，我地就全球各大機場送機！！<br />\n既然香港抗爭者會係<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港機場搞接機</span></span></strong>，咁我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">海外</span></span></strong>既巴打絲打梗係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要送機</span></span></strong>以示聲援！<br />\n<br />\n我地一班溫哥華既學生將會暫定係8號至10號於溫哥華國際機場YVR Airport內穿上示威者裝束展示標語海報。<br />\n<br />\n係上次全加國號召集會都有學生做相似Performance，以下為示意圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fyvr4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67563731_109762603704062_4570682837530836992_o.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_oc=AQk3oEEvn434ds_1EQFTp4Ow4adI6_ed8AWcmR4Gj21JvPHgnuJUfJrk1LhRYi6XshI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fyvr4-1.fna&amp;oh=e9734f56d0c5ff60727639d50e08139b&amp;oe=5DDC5466\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fyvr4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67563731_109762603704062_4570682837530836992_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_oc%3DAQk3oEEvn434ds_1EQFTp4Ow4adI6_ed8AWcmR4Gj21JvPHgnuJUfJrk1LhRYi6XshI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fyvr4-1.fna%26oh%3De9734f56d0c5ff60727639d50e08139b%26oe%3D5DDC5466&h=f17882eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我地主要目的係提醒返去香港既旅客要<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">加緊留意香港局勢</span></strong>同埋<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">幫抗爭者係海外做返PR，爭取更多外國旅客支持。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我地已經聯絡左YVR提出申請，現等候相關部門回覆。<br />\n咁我地係YVR咁細嘅機場搞，為免過份打擾其他旅客，我地預想唔會有上圖遮陣同Banner，規模會細啲，人數會少啲。但如果你地當地機場夠大、情況許可嘅，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>請大家有幾大搞幾大！</strong></span></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全球一齊集氣聲勢絕對唔可以輸蝕！</span></span></strong><br />\n最差情況如果機場方面唔批我地一個固定既location 搞我地都會派員將標語放係行李車上面，以快閃、不擾民既方式進行。<br />\n<br />\n時間緊迫，如果要聯絡你地當機場就請盡快！<br />\n歡迎有興趣係其他機場搞既手足們PM我地，以作事前聯絡或者事後整合。<br />\n<br />\n現在我地呼籲<strong>冚球咁多位香港人</strong>，一定要：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">海外送機，<br />\n香港接機！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，<br />\n時代革命！</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:23:56.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"a10a3b249f8abf8bc4288a76665ea30fdf1e9dbb","tid":1429282,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:25:48.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n首先要釋放義士<br />\n撤回送中法案<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">即時進行雙真普選<br />\n由民選政府組織獨立調查委員會徹查</span></span></span> <br />\n<br />\n如果由777政府組織獨立調查委員會<br />\n即係自已人查自已人<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/10/123632_919fc6b46082c63b79cd8a618fae2356.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F10%2F123632_919fc6b46082c63b79cd8a618fae2356.jpg&h=7a774b62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89d568d6dea8a1331db8894cb6db80df0e42e5c7","tid":1429282,"uid":2662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:31:14.000Z","msg":"感謝<br />\n推"},{"pid":"56ce6958ad8473391c90ff499fd6f06cf39503a6","tid":1429282,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:43:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b4d1257560b884ccea6ff8f2e56d9b0d4a21e651","tid":1429282,"uid":295717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:50:13.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"4ff9fd00efaad1b64b05148de18feea89d9b9b74","tid":1429282,"uid":80373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T00:51:17.000Z","msg":"！"},{"pid":"5b98d7953c09693d7f04910c1924c6104c2deb8b","tid":1429282,"uid":241363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T03:56:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8月9至11日<br />\n乜都唔做<br />\n係機場訓！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yAkHyjb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyAkHyjb.jpg&h=150882f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ti6WCLR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTi6WCLR.jpg&h=12c6c3a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3nvDQ5S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A